There is a small typo in the lineTo overload which takes 2 GridPoint2 points as parameters:

public Array<GridPoint2> line(GridPoint2 start, GridPoint2 end) {
    return line(start.x, start.y, end.y, end.y);
}

end.y is being passed as parameter twice. This made me scratch my head for a while. 

Would have raised a PR had this not been such a simple thing.

